text: Woltersdorf (Nuthe-Urstromtal) station is a railway station in the municipality of Woltersdorf (Nuthe-Urstromtal), located in the Teltow-Fläming district in Brandenburg, Germany. ==References== ==External links== Category:Railway stations in Brandenburg Category:Buildings and structures in Teltow-Fläming
